For An Act To Be Entitled
8
9 AN ACT TO REQUIRE A LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICER WHO IS
10 EXECUTING OR SERVING AN ORDER OF PROTECTION TO SERVE
11 ANY OUTSTANDING CRIMINAL WARRANTS RELATED TO DOMESTIC
12 VIOLENCE OR OFFENSES IN WHICH THE PETITIONER FOR THE
13 ORDER OF PROTECTION IS THE VICTIM OF THE OFFENSE
14 SPECIFIED IN THE WARRANT; AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES.
